"{\"uid\": \"newcountry1079.iheart.com-featured-scott-stevens-content-2024-08-12-restaurant-names-burger-after-olympic-runner-noah-lyles\", \"text\": \"Want to know more about Scott Stevens? Get his official bio, social pages and articles on New Country 107.9 YYD!Full Bio  Burger of the Month is a restaurant in Alexandria, Virginia, and they are celebrating of their own. Fellow Alexandrian, Olympic runnerNoah Lyles, is being honored by having a burger named after him. The burger features \\\"a mix of angus beef, cheddar, bacon, sweet bread and butter pickles, lettuce, tomato, ranch, on a brioche bun.\\\" As an added bonus, while the Noah Lyles burger is available, anyone who finishes it in under 9.79 seconds will get it free!  Source:AlxNow.com\"}"